            <title>Textron Marine &amp; Land Systems attains CMMI Maturity Level 3</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems, an operating unit of Textron Systems, a Textron Inc. company, announced January 10 that it has been appraised at a Capability Maturity Model Integration (CMMI) Maturity Level 3.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	CMMI Maturity Level 3 Certification is an internationally recognized process improvement maturity model given to organizations with rigorous and modern product development and services practices. Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems demonstrated industry best practices, cohesively integrating management, engineering and technology activities across its operations. Through the use of CMMI, Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems has established a framework for guiding product development and quality while reducing product costs through reliable, repeatable processes across all departments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;quot;This designation, which is respected around the world, is an extraordinary achievement that reflects our world-class performance capabilities and the high quality mind-set across our organization,&amp;rdquo; said Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems general manager Tom Walmsley. &amp;ldquo;This certification clearly validates the maturity of our engineering and program management processes to assure success on large Acquisition Category (ACAT) I programs like the U.S. Navy&amp;rsquo;s Ship-to-Shore Connector (SSC) program.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;ldquo;Obtaining CMMI Level 3 demonstrates that we, as an organization, are dedicated to applying the program management and engineering excellence required to produce superior designs, products and services for our current and future customers,&amp;rdquo; said Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems vice president of engineering Robert Foss.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	In addition to CMMI Level 3, Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems is a Six Sigma and ISO 9000 certified organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;About Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems specializes in the design, production and support of advanced marine craft, armored combat vehicles, turrets and related subsystems. Through its MillenWorks strategic business, Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems designs and develops advanced mobility solutions for demanding on- and off-road applications. Textron Marine &amp;amp; Land Systems serves military and commercial customers domestically and internationally, and is an operating unit of Textron Systems, a Textron Inc. company.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/six_sigma/~4/NEa392NwW_g" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
