            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Ken McGuire, the president/founder of Management Excellence Action Coalition, provides the plenary speech a recent U.S.-China manufacturing conference. Ken is recognized for expertise on global competitiveness issues, particularly lean manufacturing, Total Quality Management and Six Sigma production systems. He has initiated a educational awareness program &amp;quot;MeetChinaBiz - New England&amp;quot; to assist small- and medium-sized manufacturing businesses help each other help themselves to address the &amp;quot;China challenge&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
